{"thi-ap39:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap39:0.2":"Khattiyavagga ","thi-ap39:0.3":"9 Ambapalitheriapadana ","thi-ap39:1.1":"“Yo ramsiphusitavelo, ","thi-ap39:1.2":"phusso nama mahamuni; ","thi-ap39:1.3":"Tassaham bhagini asim, ","thi-ap39:1.4":"ajayim khattiye kule. ","thi-ap39:2.1":"Tassa dhammam sunitvaham, ","thi-ap39:2.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","thi-ap39:2.3":"Mahadanam daditvana, ","thi-ap39:2.4":"patthayim rupasampadam. ","thi-ap39:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","thi-ap39:3.2":"sikhi lokagganayako; ","thi-ap39:3.3":"Uppanno lokapajjoto, ","thi-ap39:3.4":"tilokasarano jino. ","thi-ap39:4.1":"Tadarunapure ramme, ","thi-ap39:4.2":"brahmannakulasambhava; ","thi-ap39:4.3":"Vimuttacittam kupita, ","thi-ap39:4.4":"bhikkhunim abhisapayim. ","thi-ap39:5.1":"‘Vesikava anacara’, ","thi-ap39:5.2":"jinasasanadusika; ","thi-ap39:5.3":"Evam akkosayitvana, ","thi-ap39:5.4":"tena papena kammuna. ","thi-ap39:6.1":"Darunam nirayam gantva, ","thi-ap39:6.2":"mahadukkhasamappita; ","thi-ap39:6.3":"Tato cuta manussesu, ","thi-ap39:6.4":"upapanna tapassini. ","thi-ap39:7.1":"Dasajatisahassani, ","thi-ap39:7.2":"ganikattamakarayim; ","thi-ap39:7.3":"Tamha papa na muccissam, ","thi-ap39:7.4":"bhutva dutthavisam yatha. ","thi-ap39:8.1":"Brahmacariyamasevissam, ","thi-ap39:8.2":"kassape jinasasane; ","thi-ap39:8.3":"Tena kammavipakena, ","thi-ap39:8.4":"ajayim tidase pure. ","thi-ap39:9.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","thi-ap39:9.2":"ahosim opapatika; ","thi-ap39:9.3":"Ambasakhantare jata, ","thi-ap39:9.4":"ambapaliti tenaham. ","thi-ap39:10.1":"Parivuta panakotihi, ","thi-ap39:10.2":"pabbajim jinasasane; ","thi-ap39:10.3":"Pattaham acalam thanam, ","thi-ap39:10.4":"dhita buddhassa orasa. ","thi-ap39:11.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap39:11.2":"sotadhatuvisuddhiya; ","thi-ap39:11.3":"Cetopariyananassa, ","thi-ap39:11.4":"vasi homi mahamuni. ","thi-ap39:12.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap39:12.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap39:12.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap39:12.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap39:13.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","thi-ap39:13.2":"patibhane tatheva ca; ","thi-ap39:13.3":"Nanam me vimalam suddham, ","thi-ap39:13.4":"buddhasetthassa vahasa. ","thi-ap39:14.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap39:14.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap39:14.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap39:15.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap39:15.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap39:15.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap39:16.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap39:16.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap39:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap39:17.1":"Ittham sudam ambapali bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap39:18.1":"Ambapalitheriyapadanam navamam. "}